.SH LIMITATIONS\"{{{
The tokens recognized by the program correspond only to a subset of
the keywords of ZBasic for Apple II. They were deduced from
examination of a few sample tokenized program. Tokens for which a
keyword has not been identified will appear as a $ sign followed by an
hexadecimal number. Knowing the list of keywords of Zbasic and their
syntax may allow identification of the missing tokens. 
.\"}}}
